,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"黑龍江省農業委員會日前召開專題會議，向省內各市下達了2018年全省擴種大豆及新增耕地輪作試點任務表。具體擴種面積官方尚未公佈。<br />\n<br />\n吉林省也於日前召開了全省調整種植業結構擴大大豆種植面積工作視頻會議並下發《關於下達2018年全省大豆種植面積任務的通知》。相關人士稱，4月27日，國家召開相關專題會議，明確提出要擴大大豆種植面積，黑龍江省是國家確定的承擔任務省份之一。（澎湃）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wallstreetcn.com/livenews/1250071?ivk=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwallstreetcn.com%2Flivenews%2F1250071%3Fivk%3D1&d=hAgi6XNAq8QbtBb1FsP%2BS4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3ad69d08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wallstreetcn.com/livenews/1250071?ivk=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398869f4bc0d03bfd463e451c3eca7a62e4ed0e7","tid":651391,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3098766c1084995c899fe23fc085b7bac928a6","tid":651391,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贏國以為美國佬真係仲想靠佢"}]}